e safety of our staff on 5th August Strike<br />\n<br />\nContent <br />\nDear Management of ___________,  <br />\n<br />\nAccording to sources as diverse as newspaper headlines (see attached link below) and various discussions on Facebook and web forums, a major strike is expected on 5th August (next Monday), with large scale assembly is also expected in our area. I am worried for both public safety and public transportation logistics for the day. <br />\n<br />\nAccording to OCCUPATIONAL SAFETY AND HEALTH ORDINANCE, CHAPTER 509, Employers should contribute to safety and health in their workplaces by: <br />\n* providing and maintaining safe access to and egress from the workplaces; and <br />\n* providing and maintaining a safe and healthy work environment <br />\n<br />\nMay I seek a clarification on management&rsquo;s plan?<br />\n<br />\nWill there be any disciplinary action if the employee decided to join the strike on 5 August 2019?<br />\n<br />\nNews- HK protesters call for citywide strike on August 5<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asiatimes.com%2F2019%2F07%2Farticle%2Fhk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5&d=7fFLqiM2ByXH61viL1oyjJugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=12f71201\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asiatimes.com/2019/07/article/hk-protesters-call-for-citywide-strike-on-august-5</a>"},{"pid":"7cf80724e4c9bb765b76fdee7d5a84e192632584","tid":1396304,"uid":284538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bda0252d1b55f169f733755f053a2e82b5eff09","tid":1396304,"uid":284538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d797716c599dbfb9e41402d943828af4f1044a02","tid":1396304,"uid":284538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:03:49.000Z","msg":"共黨國慶前送到！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T05:04:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"h